title: The Last 4 Quartets - Schubert EAC-FLAC *Includes Scans+Log*
description:
Another fine Audio Rip from the excellent CD Audio collection of my grandfather

The Last Four Quartets

By Franz Schubert

Performed By the Quartetto Italiano

A Stereo Philips "Classics," Digitally Remastered in 1995, Originally recorded in 1966 and 1977.

Included in the torrent is an EAC rip log, plus the original scans of the CD and Booklets
